thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by Lily

author: Lily
title: Lily
text: This was my first time ordering from American Frame. At first I was hesitant about the cost but it was completely worth it. They have a great variety of options for custom framing and other materials that I thought I would have to buy somewhere else. I was pleased with the shipping time, quality of materials, and packaging. Assembly was easy and painless.
